    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies to deliver instantaneous throttle response through a 7-speed M-Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) with Drivelogic. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal lateral grip and corner-exit traction. This example retains its weight-saving carbon fiber roof, lowering the center of gravity for improved roll gradient. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator servicing, ensuring the mechanical assembly remains within tight tolerances. The exterior and interior exhibit minor patina consistent with regular enthusiast use, but the powertrain and subframe remain structurally sound and performance-ready.",
      "price": 34500.0,
